1
00:00:24,330 --> 00:00:25,130
My lady.

2
00:00:27,860 --> 00:00:28,390
Fushufu.

3
00:00:38,060 --> 00:00:39,860
This is a fairy.

4
00:00:43,660 --> 00:00:45,130
Kill all the men on the spot.

5
00:00:45,130 --> 00:00:46,060
And take the women back.

6
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:47,260
Charge, brothers!

7
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:50,700
Don't be afraid. I'm here.

8
00:01:24,930 --> 00:01:26,600
The Art of War says,

9
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:27,660
a commander

10
00:01:27,830 --> 00:01:31,300
stands for wisdom, credibility, benevolence, courage, and strictness.

11
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:32,900
You have talent and ruthlessness,

12
00:01:32,900 --> 00:01:34,400
but a true commander

13
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,900
cannot be made solely by ruthlessness and courage.

14
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:37,930
From today on,

15
00:01:37,930 --> 00:01:39,900
you must carefully read two military books every ten days.

16
00:01:39,900 --> 00:01:41,530
I will test you myself at the end of the month.

17
00:01:41,530 --> 00:01:42,729
If you slack off at all,

18
00:01:42,729 --> 00:01:44,130
you will be grounded for three months

19
00:01:44,130 --> 00:01:45,330
and forbidden from entering my courtyard.

20
00:01:45,330 --> 00:01:46,130
Yes.

21
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,020
I'll do whatever my lady says.

22
00:01:48,630 --> 00:01:49,500
Her old boudoir friends

23
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,630
actually all know about my existence.

24
00:01:51,729 --> 00:01:53,660
They even say we are deeply in love.

25
00:01:54,130 --> 00:01:56,360
She must have told them secretly.

26
00:01:57,229 --> 00:02:00,560
You did have feelings for me back then, didn't you?

27
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,930
No, I didn't.

28
00:02:05,330 --> 00:02:06,230
I knew it.

29
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,130
You couldn't possibly

30
00:02:08,130 --> 00:02:09,460
just be playing with me.

31
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:11,430
And to think I was wondering on my way here

32
00:02:11,430 --> 00:02:13,600
how to try my best to make him happy,

33
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:16,560
so he would propose to Wei Er as soon as possible.

34
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,960
I didn't expect this fool

35
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,829
to be coaxed so easily

36
00:02:19,829 --> 00:02:21,530
by Wei Er's few humiliating words.

37
00:02:21,530 --> 00:02:23,660
It's really both maddening and funny.

38
00:02:24,329 --> 00:02:25,460
Lu Jingxing.

39
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,730
Forget it. In this situation,

40
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:30,860
I can't bring myself to tell him to marry Wei Yingying as soon as possible.

41
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:32,660
Let him be happy for this moment.

42
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:50,360
His Majesty has reprimanded you repeatedly these past few days, Father.

43
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:52,060
What exactly is the reason?

44
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,000
Before the late Emperor passed away,

45
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,060
he summoned me secretly,

46
00:02:56,060 --> 00:03:00,320
and ordered me to secretly search for his youngest son left among the people.

47
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:05,430
The late Emperor has a biological son?

48
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,960
But when the current Emperor ascended the throne,

49
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,030
he clearly declared to the public

50
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:10,300
that the late Emperor had no son.

51
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:11,460
So the younger brother succeeded the elder brother,

52
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:14,120
and he, as the younger brother, took the throne.

53
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,930
This is the secret edict left by the late Emperor,

54
00:03:16,930 --> 00:03:20,460
ordering me to read it in public after finding the young prince.

55
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:21,400
But now,

56
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:24,960
His Majesty already knows about the existence of this edict.

57
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:27,960
I'm afraid our Shen family is about to face a disaster.

58
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:30,460
Father.

59
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,430
Lu Jingxing is brave and resourceful,

60
00:03:33,430 --> 00:03:34,630
and careful despite his rough exterior.

61
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:35,230
Given time,

62
00:03:35,230 --> 00:03:36,960
he will definitely achieve great things.

63
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,000
Go with him.

64
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:39,720
Leave while you still can.

65
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,630
I have enjoyed

66
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:45,760
the honor and protection of being the eldest daughter of the Shen family since childhood.

67
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:48,820
So naturally I must bear the due responsibilities now.

68
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:51,560
You are a loyal subject of the country, Father.

69
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,760
And I am also a pillar of the Shen family.

70
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:55,960
I will never flee before the battle

71
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,220
or abandon our family.

72
00:03:57,530 --> 00:03:58,590
If you don't leave,

73
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:01,490
Lu Jingxing definitely won't leave either.

74
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,800
Are you going to drag him down

75
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:05,400
and let him be destroyed by this disaster too?

76
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,130
I will make my own decision.

77
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:11,800
I definitely won't put him in a dilemma.

78
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,089
Why are you sighing?

79
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,660
Was I too reckless last night

80
00:04:20,899 --> 00:04:21,760
and hurt you?

81
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:26,800
Lu Jingxing.

82
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,820
What are your orders, My Lady?

83
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:33,320
Can you propose to Wei Yingying as soon as possible?

84
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:35,500
Shen Lvyi,

85
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:38,000
what treasure do you want from the Grand Tutor's mansion?

86
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,860
You are not mad at me for using you?

87
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:41,530
What's the use of being mad?

88
00:04:41,530 --> 00:04:43,030
You'll just quietly regret it for a while

89
00:04:43,030 --> 00:04:45,330
and then find someone else to use.

90
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,460
Instead of having other men around you,

91
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:48,659
I'd rather it be me.

92
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:56,900
He is now His Majesty's trusted right-hand man

93
00:04:56,930 --> 00:04:58,100
and highly favored.

94
00:04:58,100 --> 00:05:00,960
If he knew I was looking for the late Emperor's will,

95
00:05:01,130 --> 00:05:02,960
wouldn't that put him in a dilemma

96
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,260
between His Majesty and me?

97
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:05,660
On one side is the Emperor's favor,

98
00:05:05,660 --> 00:05:06,900
and on the other is our past affection.

99
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,500
No matter what he chooses,

100
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,060
he won't escape a bad fate.

101
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,800
He cannot know about this.

102
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:16,300
Lu Jingxing, if you want to be used by me,

103
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:17,800
don't ask why.

104
00:05:18,330 --> 00:05:19,460
If you don't want to,

105
00:05:20,230 --> 00:05:21,430
since I am heartless,

106
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,700
you can just leave.

107
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,360
If I could choose,

108
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,460
I wouldn't want to be so lowly,

109
00:05:26,730 --> 00:05:27,530
being called by you at will

110
00:05:27,530 --> 00:05:28,730
and dismissed at will.

111
00:05:28,730 --> 00:05:29,930
But I am willing.

112
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:32,030
Even if I have to die for you again,

113
00:05:32,030 --> 00:05:33,290
even a thousand times.

114
00:05:34,030 --> 00:05:35,630
As long as you look at me,

115
00:05:35,630 --> 00:05:36,730
I am willing.

116
00:05:37,030 --> 00:05:38,159
Where are you going?

117
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,300
To wake Lu Zhong up

118
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,600
and buy those damn betrothal gifts at the market.

119
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,930
Shen Lvyi, let me tell you,

120
00:05:42,930 --> 00:05:44,330
I haven't forgiven you yet.

121
00:05:44,330 --> 00:05:45,260
From now on,

122
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,560
if you dare abandon me for anyone or anything else,

123
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,400
I swear I'll never demean myself again

124
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:51,000
and never obey you again.

125
00:05:58,630 --> 00:05:59,430
Shen Lvyi.

126
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:00,500
That bitch.

127
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,800
When she was the young lady of the Minister's mansion,

128
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,600
she always stole my spotlight.

129
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:07,700
Now she has been reduced to a lowly maid,

130
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,100
yet she dares to steal my fiancé.

131
00:06:12,730 --> 00:06:16,230
It's also your fault for showing off.

132
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:18,060
To humiliate her,

133
00:06:18,230 --> 00:06:21,100
you insisted on buying her as a test-marriage maid.

134
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:22,530
Look what happened now.

135
00:06:22,530 --> 00:06:23,830
You invited a wolf into the house.

136
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:26,130
General Weibei happens to like her

137
00:06:26,330 --> 00:06:27,790
and insists on having her.

138
00:06:28,330 --> 00:06:30,060
Otherwise, with my temper,

139
00:06:30,460 --> 00:06:32,600
I would have married her to the horse slave long ago,

140
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,800
letting her suffer

141
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,400
and be ruined to death.

142
00:06:37,730 --> 00:06:40,100
General Weibei fancies her.

143
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:45,130
What if she degrades herself?

144
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,000
You mean...

145
00:06:48,460 --> 00:06:49,700
Drug her

146
00:06:49,930 --> 00:06:51,800
and call the horse slave, Lai Mazi.

147
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,060
When they are having sex

148
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:55,330
and completely out of it, arrange for

149
00:06:55,330 --> 00:06:56,960
General Weibei to catch them.

150
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,130
I don't believe

151
00:06:58,130 --> 00:06:58,800
Lu Jingxing,

152
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,460
the dignified General Weibei,

153
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:01,560
His Majesty's favorite,

154
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,360
such a glorious big shot,

155
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,400
can tolerate being cuckolded.

156
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:07,700
My good daughter,

157
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,260
you really have your ways.

158
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:10,520
We'll do just that.

159
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,860
I'll go arrange it now.
